CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.ProductProvider`
(
  ProductProviderId STRING NOT NULL,
  ProductProviderName STRING(100) NOT NULL,
  ProductProviderTypeId STRING NOT NULL,
  Address STRING(150),
  City STRING(150),
  StateRegion STRING(50),
  PostalCode STRING(16),
  PhoneNumber STRING(30),
  FaxNumber STRING(30),
  Inactive BOOL NOT NULL,
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
